{"tid":541732,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"36E陳婉嫻行性感唔夠姣被嫌棄","createTime":"2018-01-26T18:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T05:32:44.000Z","uid":157545,"like":33,"dislike":217,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"a032a19afed221b815c1a1138dc5d775ba07be41","tid":541732,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T18:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180126/photo/bkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_05b.jpg?20180126101909\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20180126101909&h=e4baf9c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擁有36E強勁身材的「咪神」陳婉衡（Alycia）去年在多部電影中分別飾演性格截然不同的角色，首次挑戰喊戲及打戲，並在賀歲片《我的情敵女婿》中客串演最拿手的性感尤物，問到最難演繹的是哪種角色？身材出眾的她竟表示是Sell性感：「最難係性感呀！其實我真人一啲都唔女人，好粗魯，有時拍戲嗰陣大家叫我再姣啲，我就將僅餘嘅女人味挖出嚟，依家明白做戲唔係做自己，所以要忘記本身幾咁粗魯。」<br />\n<br />\n開槍搞到有幻聽<br />\n<br />\n至於最喜愛的角色類型，Alycia直言拍完警匪片後愛上做打女，希望有機會繼續鑽研電影動作：「除咗打戲，仲有拎真機關槍，有次唔記得咗戴耳塞就開槍，隻耳仔幻聽咗幾日，不過都冇驚咗拍動作片，惟有之後再小心啲！」<br />\n<br />\n做KOL教Keep Fit<br />\n<br />\n此外，經常運動及旅遊的Alycia計劃踩過界做KOL，拍片與Fans分享這兩個範疇的樂趣，她說：「不時有人私訊我問我點做運動，我可能拍吓片教大家點Keep Fit，點樣喺屋企做啲簡單嘅運動，仲有煮健康餐，有時將自己生活習慣轉變少少，就有好大分別，其實Keep Fit唔係咁難嘅事，每日都可以做到。」Alycia表示她在青春期時其實頗有肉地，而且懶做運動，直至入行後為加強體能應付拍攝，才開始做運動，其後愈來愈上癮愛上操肌，她直言可以將心得跟觀眾分享。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180126/photo/bkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_06b.jpg?20180126101909\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20180126101909&h=bca450ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180126/photo/bkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_12b.jpg?20180126101909\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_12b.jpg%3F20180126101909&h=70295ebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180126/photo/bkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_03b.jpg?20180126101909\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20180126101909&h=5487ab97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180126/photo/bkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_02b.jpg?20180126101909\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20180126101909&h=d5a2ceb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180126/photo/bkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_11b.jpg?20180126101909\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_11b.jpg%3F20180126101909&h=2837f796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180126/photo/bkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_08b.jpg?20180126101909\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180126074423146-0126_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20180126101909&h=de943e01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3630131f478cea25b0142314cf1f019b3686a52c","tid":541732,"uid":13467,"like":547,"dislike":23,"score":524,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T18:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130614/photo/0614-00176-021v1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20130614%2Fphoto%2F0614-00176-021v1.jpg&h=6feb199f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"444b747414c0dc6c3d5d7473f25cfc76609bcc8a","tid":541732,"uid":53498,"like":20,"dislike":75,"score":-5